《'''酷瓜人生'''》 ({{lang-fr|'''Ma vie de Courgette'''}})是一部2016年法国和瑞士合拍的[[定格动画|定格动画]]电影，为[[瑞士|瑞士]]导演[[克劳德·巴拉斯|克劳德·巴拉斯]]执导的首部动画长片<ref name="stop">{{cite web|url=http://www.swissinfo.ch/eng/best-foreign-film-_animated-film-to-represent-switzerland-at-oscars/42354912 |title=Animated film to represent Switzerland at Oscars |work=Swissinfo |date=5 August 2016 |accessdate=5 August 2016}}</ref>，改编自Gilles Paris所写的2002年小说 ''Autobiographie d'une Courgette''。入围[[2016年坎城影展|2016年坎城影展]]导演双周单元<ref name="Quinzaine">{{cite web |url=http://www.quinzaine-realisateurs.com/en/fortnight-2016/ |title=Fortnight 2016: The 48th Directors' Fortnight Selection |accessdate=19 April 2016 |work=Quinzaine des Réalisateurs |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160420130803/http://www.quinzaine-realisateurs.com/en/fortnight-2016/ |archivedate=2016-04-20}}</ref><ref name="Quinzaine-deadline">{{cite web |url=http://deadline.com/2016/04/cannes-directors-fortnight-2016-films-lineup-full-list-1201740068/ |title=Cannes: Directors’ Fortnight 2016 Lineup – Laura Poitras’ ‘Risk’, Pablo Larrain’s ‘Neruda’, Paul Schrader’s ‘Dog Eat Dog’ |author=Nancy Tartaglione |date=19 April 2016 |accessdate=19 April 2016 |work=Deadline Hollywood |archive-date=2019-03-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190328112344/https://deadline.com/2016/04/cannes-directors-fortnight-2016-films-lineup-full-list-1201740068/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。获得[[第89届奥斯卡金像奖|第89届奥斯卡金像奖]]最佳动画长片提名<ref name="BestAni">{{Cite news|url=http://www.oscars.org/oscars/ceremonies/2017|title=2017|newspaper=Oscars.org {{!}} Academy of Motion Picture Arts and Sciences|language=en|access-date=24 January 2017|archive-date=2017-03-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170303235233/https://www.oscars.org/oscars/ceremonies/2017|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="Switzerland">{{cite web |url=http://variety.com/2016/film/global/switzerland-claude-barras-my-life-as-a-courgette-foreign-languageoscarrace-1201831359/ |title=Switzerland Sends Claude Barras’s ‘My Life as a Courgette’ to Foreign-Language Oscar Race |last=Keslassy |first=Elsa |work=[[Variety_(magazine)|Variety]] |date=5 August 2016 |accessdate=5 August 2016 |archive-date=2016-08-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160818201828/http://variety.com/2016/film/global/switzerland-claude-barras-my-life-as-a-courgette-foreign-languageoscarrace-1201831359/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>，赢得[[欧洲电影奖|欧洲电影奖]]最佳动画片，[[第42届凯萨奖|第42届凯萨奖]]最佳改编剧本和最佳动画片。

== 剧情 ==
九歲小男孩酷瓜，失去了相依為命的媽媽，被安置在收容所，和一群無家可歸的小朋友一同生活。一天，收容所來了一位10歲的新女孩卡蜜，她的開朗點亮了院裡的氣氛，也讓酷瓜第一次有了心動的感覺。正當大家相處越來越融洽時，卡蜜的阿姨突然出現，為了大筆撫養金和收容所爭取撫養權。一場保衛卡蜜大作戰正式展開。

==反响==
影片在[[烂番茄|烂番茄]]上的好评度为98%<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/my_life_as_a_zucchini/|title=My Life as a Zucchini (Ma vie de courgette)|publisher=|accessdate=10 January 2017}}</ref>，在[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]上获得85分<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.metacritic.com/movie/my-life-as-a-zucchini|title=My Life as a Zucchini (Ma Vie de Courgette)|publisher=|accessdate=10 January 2017}}</ref>。

